ESCO dataset attribution
-------------------------

This package may ship or reference CSV extracts from ESCO (European Skills,
Competences, Qualifications and Occupations), maintained by the European
Commission. ESCO content is subject to the legal notice and licensing terms
published at:

  https://esco.ec.europa.eu/en/about-esco/legal-notice

When redistributing ESCO-derived data, comply with those terms and retain
appropriate attribution. This project’s MIT license applies to the Python
code only, not to third-party taxonomy data.
